  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0d9c\u0dd1\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d8b\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9 50 \u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The suspect who stole 50 tear gas bullets was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Mr. Nihal Talduwa said that a person who attacked three police officers and stole 50 teargas canisters has been arrested by the Welikada Police at Nanayakkara Mawatha, Welikada Obeysekarapura.",
        "The hijacked stock of air bullets has been found hidden in the house where the suspect temporarily resides on Borella Gotami Road.",
        "On the night of the 13th last night, when the police and the army worked together to control the protest held at the Polduwa intersection in the Welikada police domain, three police officers who were carrying tear gas canisters in a three-wheeler were attacked and the tear gas canisters in their custody were stolen, the media spokesman said. added.",
        "The arrested suspect working as a mason is a 31-year-old resident of Polonnaruwa Kashyapa Pura.",
        "The suspect is to be presented to the court Welikada Police is conducting investigations."
      ],
